{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-1b472bc8-38c2-4866-b29e-2421e891a6c3","sequence":2357,"parentEventId":"evt-381c5fd3-3edb-4d4d-86c6-08d66a205ee9","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100780","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Author unified-idea-plan.schema.json and brainstorm-session.schema.json. Produce four progressive validation fixtures. All fixtures pass schema validation.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-1D (1.4) — Unified IdeaPlan envelope schema, brainstorm-session record schema, and four validation fixtures\n\nApproach:\nAuthor schemas/ideas/unified-idea-plan.schema.json (envelope: documentId, ideaId, title, status enum, timestamps, optional brainstorm section, optional plan section, optional delivery section). Author schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json (session record: sessionId, conductedAt, agentSessionRef, all 13 sub-input fields, computed score fields, sessionNotes). Produce four progressive validation fixtures: (1) idea-only, (2) idea+brainstorm-1session, (3) idea+brainstorm-2sessions+plan-section, (4) idea+all-sections. All fixtures must pass schema validation.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- Each state has a machine-readable schema file with an agentDirective section that prescribes required agent behavior for that state — agents read the state schema and follow it, not playbook prose\n- The brainstorming state schema agentDirective defines the full agent-led session: ordered question phases, scoring sub-inputs, formula application steps, and synthesis update — agents must not invent a different flow\n- Each brainstorming session computes valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, and priorityScore using the canonical formulas defined in the schema\n- US-5\n\nTechnical scope:\n- schemas/ideas/unified-idea-plan.schema.json (new)\n- schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json (new)\n- fixtures/ideas/fixture-1-idea-only.json\n- fixtures/ideas/fixture-2-idea-brainstorm-1session.json\n- fixtures/ideas/fixture-3-idea-brainstorm-2sessions-plan.json\n- fixtures/ideas/fixture-4-idea-all-sections.json\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- unified-idea-plan.schema.json validates the envelope with status constrained to the six-state enum\n- brainstorm-session.schema.json validates a session record including all 13 sub-input fields and five computed score fields\n- All four progressive fixtures pass schema validation without errors\n- Each fixture contains only the sections appropriate for its state (no future sections leaking into earlier fixtures)\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: all four fixtures pass unified-idea-plan schema validation\n- Unit test: fixtures 2, 3, 4 pass brainstorm-session schema validation for their session records\n- Unit test: fixture-1 fails validation if a brainstorm section is injected (schema correctly rejects it at idea state)\n\nDone means:\nBoth schema files committed; four progressive fixtures pass schema validation; fixture isolation verified\n\nRisk notes:\nMechanical once the per-state schemas are established; risk is fixtures being inconsistent with the per-state schemas","approach":"Author unified-idea-plan.schema.json and brainstorm-session.schema.json. Produce four progressive validation fixtures. All fixtures pass schema validation.","dependsOn":["T100777","T100778","T100779"],"technicalScope":["schemas/ideas/unified-idea-plan.schema.json","schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json","fixtures/ideas/ (four progressive fixtures)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Both schema files validate their respective shapes","All four fixtures pass validation","Fixtures contain only sections appropriate for their state"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-1D","wbsPath":"1.4","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
