{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-b12965ea-767f-4905-a9b4-e266a47d4a1a","sequence":2359,"parentEventId":"evt-3051cd60-5da7-48fd-a4ff-13e0cab29a32","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100781","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Implement six-state machine enforcement and state-schema loader utility (given a status, returns schema path and parsed agentDirective). No new commands.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-2A (2.1) — Ideas module: six-state machine implementation and state-schema loader utility\n\nApproach:\nImplement the six-state status machine in the Ideas module SQLite layer. Expand the IdeaStatus TypeScript type to IdeaPlanStatus including all nine valid values (six new states plus three legacy aliases: open→idea, planning unchanged, planned→accepted). Enforce valid transitions per the transition table from WBS-1A; additionally allow idea→planning as a valid direct transition (skip brainstorming). Build the state-schema loader utility: given a document status string, returns the path to the correct state schema file and the parsed agentDirective object. No new commands in this task — state machine and loader only.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- The document status advances through six states: idea → brainstorming → planning → reviewed → accepted → delivered\n- Each state has a machine-readable schema file with an agentDirective section that prescribes required agent behavior for that state — agents read the state schema and follow it, not playbook prose\n- US-5\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/ideas/ (six-state machine enforcement, state-schema loader utility)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- IdeaPlanStatus type includes all six new states plus three legacy aliases; parseIdeaStatus accepts all nine values\n- Six-state machine implemented; all valid transitions succeed including idea→planning direct bypass; invalid transitions rejected with clear error message\n- State-schema loader returns the correct schema file path and a parsed agentDirective for each of the six statuses\n- State-schema loader is importable as a standalone utility by other modules\n\nVerification:\n- Unit tests: all six valid status transitions succeed; idea→planning direct bypass succeeds; at least three invalid transitions are rejected with appropriate errors\n- Unit test: state-schema loader returns correct schema path and parseable agentDirective for each of the six statuses\n- Unit test: parseIdeaStatus accepts all nine values (six new + three legacy aliases)\n\nDone means:\nSix-state machine enforces transitions in SQLite layer; state-schema loader utility committed and unit tested\n\nRisk notes:\nNo SQLite schema migration needed — the existing linked_plan_artifact column on workflow_ideas serves as the document reference; risk is transition table correctness and legacy alias handling in IdeaPlanStatus","approach":"Implement six-state machine enforcement and state-schema loader utility (given a status, returns schema path and parsed agentDirective). No new commands.","dependsOn":["T100777","T100778","T100779","T100780"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/ideas/ (state machine, state-schema loader)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Six-state machine enforces valid transitions","State-schema loader returns correct schema and agentDirective for each status","Loader importable as standalone utility"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-2A","wbsPath":"2.1","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
