{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-3177ed33-e30a-4d81-91e5-a85c065d2ae8","sequence":2361,"parentEventId":"evt-6442ab50-0068-4977-89c7-177ae03da1bb","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100782","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Implement start-brainstorm-session (transitions idea→brainstorming on first call, appends session slot on subsequent calls). Implement update-brainstorm-session (merges partial fields into session at given index). Implement scoring engine reading weights from brainstorming state schema including priorityScore normalization to 0–100.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-2B (2.2) — Ideas module: start-brainstorm-session, update-brainstorm-session commands and scoring engine\n\nApproach:\nImplement start-brainstorm-session command: when the document is in idea state, transition to brainstorming and append a session slot with { sessionIndex, startedAt }; when the document is in any other state, append a new session slot without changing status. Implement update-brainstorm-session command: given a sessionIndex and a partial session record, merges supplied fields into the session record at that index — allows the agent to write sub-inputs and computed scores incrementally during the session. Implement the scoring engine: reads formula weights from the brainstorming state schema via the state-schema loader, computes valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, and priorityScore (including normalization: rawPriority=((v×0.40)+(c×0.20)−(r×0.25)−(e×0.15))×10; priorityScore=Math.round(((rawPriority+34)/90)×100)) from session sub-inputs. Add instruction .md files for both commands.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Agent-led brainstorming sessions are stored as an ordered array on the document and can be triggered at any document status\n- Each brainstorming session computes valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, and priorityScore using the canonical formulas defined in the schema\n- The brainstorming state schema agentDirective defines the full agent-led session: ordered question phases, scoring sub-inputs, formula application steps, and synthesis update — agents must not invent a different flow\n- US-1\n- US-2\n- US-5\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/ideas/ (start-brainstorm-session command handler, update-brainstorm-session command handler, scoring engine)\n- src/modules/ideas/instructions/start-brainstorm-session.md (new)\n- src/modules/ideas/instructions/update-brainstorm-session.md (new)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- start-brainstorm-session transitions idea→brainstorming and appends first session slot { sessionIndex: 0, startedAt }\n- start-brainstorm-session on any non-idea state appends a new session slot without changing status\n- update-brainstorm-session merges supplied fields into the session record at the specified sessionIndex without replacing other fields or other sessions\n- Scoring engine reads formula weights from the brainstorming state schema (not hardcoded constants)\n- Scoring engine computes all five scores correctly including priorityScore normalization to 0–100\n- Session record is updated with all 13 sub-input fields and five computed score fields via update-brainstorm-session calls\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: start-brainstorm-session on idea-state document transitions to brainstorming and appends session slot\n- Unit test: start-brainstorm-session on planning-state document appends session slot without status change\n- Unit test: update-brainstorm-session merges fields into correct session index without affecting other sessions\n- Unit test: scoring engine produces correct valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, priorityScore (0–100) for known inputs\n- Unit test: scoring engine reads weights from schema file — verify by mutating a weight in schema and confirming output changes\n- Unit test: priorityScore normalization produces 0 at minimum inputs, 100 at maximum inputs, 50 at midpoint inputs\n\nDone means:\nstart-brainstorm-session command and scoring engine implemented; all five scores computed correctly from schema weights; instruction .md committed\n\nRisk notes:\nScoring engine correctness is the critical path; the weight-sourcing test is essential to preserve the schema-as-source-of-truth contract","approach":"Implement start-brainstorm-session (transitions idea→brainstorming on first call, appends session slot on subsequent calls). Implement update-brainstorm-session (merges partial fields into session at given index). Implement scoring engine reading weights from brainstorming state schema including priorityScore normalization to 0–100.","dependsOn":["T100781"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/ideas/ (command handlers, scoring engine)","src/modules/ideas/instructions/start-brainstorm-session.md","src/modules/ideas/instructions/update-brainstorm-session.md"],"acceptanceCriteria":["start-brainstorm-session transitions or appends correctly per current state","update-brainstorm-session merges partial fields at correct session index","Scoring engine reads weights from schema; priorityScore normalized 0–100","All five scores computed correctly for known inputs"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-2B","wbsPath":"2.2","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
