{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-c449a0b3-90d5-49c6-876a-14eea6cdffe3","sequence":2363,"parentEventId":"evt-4b3127b8-cf8a-4bc6-bc27-2e0cf884707f","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100783","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Implement complete-brainstorm (validates brainstorm section, transitions brainstorming→planning). Implement synthesis computation (60/40 recency weighting per score type, recomputed on each new session). Update get-idea to return unified document.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-2C (2.3) — Ideas module: complete-brainstorm command, session synthesis, and get-idea update\n\nApproach:\nImplement complete-brainstorm command: validates the brainstorm section (at least one session, all required fields present) and transitions document status from brainstorming to planning. Implement session synthesis: computes synthesized scores (latestSession×0.60 + mean(priorSessions)×0.40 per score type) and writes the synthesis object to brainstorm.synthesis. Synthesis is recomputed each time a new session is appended. Update get-idea to return the unified document including all sections present for the current state (brainstorm section with sessions and synthesis when in brainstorming or later states). Add instruction .md for complete-brainstorm.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- The document status advances through six states: idea → brainstorming → planning → reviewed → accepted → delivered\n- Agent-led brainstorming sessions are stored as an ordered array on the document and can be triggered at any document status\n- Each brainstorming session computes valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, and priorityScore using the canonical formulas defined in the schema\n- US-1\n- US-2\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/ideas/ (complete-brainstorm command handler, synthesis computation)\n- src/modules/ideas/instructions/complete-brainstorm.md (new)\n- src/modules/ideas/ (get-idea update to return unified document structure)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- complete-brainstorm validates brainstorm section and transitions brainstorming→planning\n- complete-brainstorm rejects transition if brainstorm section has zero sessions or missing required fields\n- Session synthesis handles N=1 correctly: synthesized scores equal the single session scores with no recency weighting\n- Session synthesis for N>=2 computes correctly: latestSession×0.60+mean(priorSessions)×0.40 per score type\n- Synthesis is recomputed and written to brainstorm.synthesis each time a new session slot is appended via start-brainstorm-session\n- get-idea returns unified document including brainstorm.sessions and brainstorm.synthesis when present\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: complete-brainstorm transitions brainstorming→planning when brainstorm section is valid\n- Unit test: complete-brainstorm rejects transition when sessions array is empty\n- Unit test: N=1 synthesis returns session scores directly without recency weighting\n- Unit test: N=2 synthesis produces expected synthesized scores with 60/40 weighting\n- Integration test: get-idea on a brainstorming-state document returns sessions array and synthesis object\n\nDone means:\ncomplete-brainstorm command implemented and tested; synthesis computation correct for single and multi-session cases; get-idea returns unified document structure\n\nRisk notes:\nSynthesis correctness for edge cases (single session, many sessions) needs explicit test coverage","approach":"Implement complete-brainstorm (validates brainstorm section, transitions brainstorming→planning). Implement synthesis computation (60/40 recency weighting per score type, recomputed on each new session). Update get-idea to return unified document.","dependsOn":["T100782"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/ideas/ (complete-brainstorm handler, synthesis, get-idea update)","src/modules/ideas/instructions/complete-brainstorm.md"],"acceptanceCriteria":["complete-brainstorm validates and transitions correctly","Synthesis computes 60/40 recency weighting correctly","get-idea returns unified document with brainstorm sections"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-2C","wbsPath":"2.3","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
