{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-35ccc3a6-8b93-448c-833d-e63162620f89","sequence":2365,"parentEventId":"evt-9ffa44c9-ad1c-4339-bf9a-4b70847d756e","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100784","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Implement check-delivery-status (queries task refs, transitions accepted→delivered on completion, returns status summary otherwise). Add Check delivery button to dashboard for accepted ideas.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-2D (2.4) — Ideas module: check-delivery-status command and delivered transition\n\nApproach:\nImplement check-delivery-status command: reads delivery.taskRefs[] from a unified document in accepted state, queries the task engine for the status of each task ref, transitions the document accepted→delivered if all tasks are completed or cancelled (minimum one completed task required). Returns a delivery status summary (total tasks, completed count, pending count, cancelled count) without transitioning when tasks are still in progress. Rejects if document is not in accepted state. Add a 'Check delivery' button to the dashboard for accepted-state ideas that calls this command and refreshes the idea card. Add instruction .md file.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Task refs and delivery refs attach to the unified document as work progresses to delivered; a check-delivery-status command transitions accepted→delivered when all delivery task refs report complete\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- US-4\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/ideas/ (check-delivery-status command handler)\n- src/modules/ideas/instructions/check-delivery-status.md (new)\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon (dashboard: Check delivery button for accepted-state ideas)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- check-delivery-status on an accepted-state document with all task refs completed or cancelled (min one completed) transitions status to delivered\n- check-delivery-status returns delivery status summary (total/completed/pending/cancelled counts) without transitioning when tasks are still in progress\n- check-delivery-status rejects if document status is not accepted\n- Dashboard shows a 'Check delivery' button for accepted-state ideas; clicking it runs check-delivery-status and refreshes the idea card\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: check-delivery-status transitions accepted→delivered when all task refs are completed or cancelled with minimum one completed\n- Unit test: check-delivery-status returns status summary without transitioning when one or more tasks are still in progress\n- Unit test: check-delivery-status rejects with clear error when document is not in accepted state\n- Extension unit test: Check delivery button renders on accepted-state idea cards and invokes check-delivery-status\n\nDone means:\ncheck-delivery-status command implemented; accepted→delivered transition working; dashboard Check delivery button renders and functions for accepted ideas\n\nRisk notes:\nTask engine query must be accessible from ideas module; use existing task-engine read commands (get-task / list-tasks) to avoid tight coupling; do not embed task-engine internals in ideas module","approach":"Implement check-delivery-status (queries task refs, transitions accepted→delivered on completion, returns status summary otherwise). Add Check delivery button to dashboard for accepted ideas.","dependsOn":["T100787"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/ideas/ (check-delivery-status handler)","src/modules/ideas/instructions/check-delivery-status.md","extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon (Check delivery button)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Transitions accepted→delivered when all task refs complete","Returns status summary without transitioning when tasks in progress","Rejects if not in accepted state","Dashboard Check delivery button renders and functions"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-2D","wbsPath":"2.4","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
