ding rubric updates, accept-plan-artifact command handler)\n- src/modules/planning/instructions/review-plan-artifact.md (updated)\n- src/modules/planning/instructions/accept-plan-artifact.md (updated)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- review-plan-artifact reads plan section from unified document and transitions status planning→reviewed\n- accept-plan-artifact reads plan section from unified document and transitions status reviewed→accepted\n- Both commands reject if the document is not in the correct predecessor state\n- review-plan-artifact rubric goal-coverage and story-coverage checks reference the unified document's goals and userStories arrays\n- External argv shapes for both commands remain backward-compatible\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: review-plan-artifact transitions planning→reviewed on unified document\n- Unit test: accept-plan-artifact transitions reviewed→accepted on unified document\n- Unit test: review-plan-artifact rejects if document status is not planning\n- Unit test: rubric correctly identifies missing goal coverage from the unified document goals array\n- Regression test: existing argv shapes still accepted\n\nDone means:\nreview and accept commands operate on unified document; status transitions planning→reviewed→accepted enforced; instruction files updated\n\nRisk notes:\nState transition guards are critical; test rejection cases explicitly","approach":"Update review-plan-artifact (transitions planning→reviewed) and accept-plan-artifact (transitions reviewed→accepted) to operate on unified document plan section. Preserve argv shapes. Update instruction files.","dependsOn":["T100785"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/planning/ (review and accept command handlers)","src/modules/planning/instructions/ (updated instruction files)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["review transitions planning→reviewed on unified document","accept transitions reviewed→accepted on unified document","Both reject incorrect predecessor states","Backward-compatible argv shapes"],"phase"