tus is not accepted\n- External argv shape for finalize-plan-to-phase remains backward-compatible\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: finalize-plan-to-phase writes task refs to unified document delivery section\n- Unit test: finalize-plan-to-phase rejects if document not in accepted state\n- Regression test: existing argv shape still accepted\n\nDone means:\nfinalize-plan-to-phase writes task refs and delivery refs to unified document delivery section; document status remains accepted after finalize; instruction file updated\n\nRisk notes:\nfinalize-plan-to-phase must only write task refs to the delivery section; the accepted→delivered transition is owned by check-delivery-status (WBS-2D) — do not duplicate that logic here","approach":"Update finalize-plan-to-phase to write task refs to unified document delivery section only — no status transition (accepted→delivered is handled by check-delivery-status). Preserve argv shape.","dependsOn":["T100786"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/planning/ (finalize-plan-to-phase handler)","src/modules/planning/instructions/finalize-plan-to-phase.md"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Task refs written to unified document delivery section","Document status remains accepted after finalize-plan-to-phase (no transition)","Rejects if not in accepted state","Backward-compatible argv shape"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-3C","wbsPath":"3.3","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
