{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-fec5c1eb-3745-4df4-bc45-6f09ad83f4c8","sequence":2373,"parentEventId":"evt-8c7710d9-4fd3-4c10-a00a-66e61584e39b","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100788","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Extend dashboard-summary projection to include brainstorm.synthesis fields and brainstormingIdeas rollup for ideas in brainstorming state. Update fixture. Backend only.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-4A (4.1) — Extend dashboard-summary projection to expose brainstorm.synthesis fields\n\nApproach:\nExtend the dashboard-summary command projection to include brainstorm.synthesis fields (valueScore, riskScore, effortScore, confidenceScore, priorityScore, sessionCount) for ideas in brainstorming state. Add a brainstormingIdeas rollup section to the dashboard-summary output that aggregates ideas in brainstorming state with their synthesis scores. This is a backend-only change — no webview changes in this task.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- The dashboard surfaces a Brainstorm button and a Brainstorming rollup showing synthesized scores (Value, Risk, Effort, Confidence, Priority) for ideas in brainstorming state\n- US-3\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/ideas/ (dashboard-summary projection update)\n- fixtures/ideas/ (update dashboard-summary fixture to include brainstorming rollup)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- dashboard-summary output includes brainstorm.synthesis fields for ideas in brainstorming state\n- dashboard-summary output includes a brainstormingIdeas rollup section with all brainstorming-state ideas and their synthesis scores\n- dashboard-summary fixture updated to include the new brainstorming rollup section\n- No webview changes in this task\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: dashboard-summary projection includes brainstorm.synthesis fields for a brainstorming-state idea fixture\n- Unit test: brainstormingIdeas rollup section aggregates all brainstorming-state ideas correctly\n\nDone means:\ndashboard-summary projection exposes brainstorm.synthesis fields and brainstormingIdeas rollup; fixture updated; no webview changes\n\nRisk notes:\nBackend only; keep it focused on projection changes; do not touch webview in this task","approach":"Extend dashboard-summary projection to include brainstorm.synthesis fields and brainstormingIdeas rollup for ideas in brainstorming state. Update fixture. Backend only.","dependsOn":["T100783"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/ideas/ (dashboard-summary projection)","fixtures/ideas/ (dashboard-summary fixture)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["brainstorm.synthesis fields in dashboard-summary for brainstorming-state ideas","brainstormingIdeas rollup section in dashboard-summary output","Fixture updated"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-4A","wbsPath":"4.1","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
