{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-1baea948-1f44-4629-bd39-9a0a6b5bd6c0","sequence":2377,"parentEventId":"evt-69f392b3-46f0-44c7-9d41-c8f956f5996e","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100790","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Add Brainstorming rollup (replacing New plan rollup) reading from brainstormingIdeas projection section. Display five scores. Update detail panel to show session history.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-4C (4.3) — Dashboard: Brainstorming rollup with scoring display and idea detail panel session history\n\nApproach:\nAdd a Brainstorming rollup to the dashboard (replacing the New plan rollup) that reads from the brainstormingIdeas rollup section of the dashboard-summary projection. Display Value, Risk, Effort, Confidence, and Priority scores per idea in the rollup. Update the idea detail panel to show brainstorm session history (per-session scores and synthesized scores) for ideas with at least one session.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- The dashboard surfaces a Brainstorm button and a Brainstorming rollup showing synthesized scores (Value, Risk, Effort, Confidence, Priority) for ideas in brainstorming state\n- US-3\n\nTechnical scope:\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon (dashboard webview: add Brainstorming rollup, replace New plan rollup)\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon (idea detail panel: add brainstorm session history display)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- Brainstorming rollup appears on the dashboard in place of the New plan rollup\n- Rollup displays all ideas in brainstorming state with Value, Risk, Effort, Confidence, and Priority scores from brainstorm.synthesis\n- Idea detail panel shows brainstorm session history with per-session scores when sessions are present\n- Idea detail panel shows synthesized scores (brainstorm.synthesis) when multiple sessions are present\n\nVerification:\n- Extension unit test: Brainstorming rollup renders with correct scores from dashboard-summary projection fixture\n- Extension unit test: rollup shows all brainstorming-state ideas from the projection\n- Extension unit test: detail panel session history renders per-session and synthesized scores\n\nDone means:\nBrainstorming rollup live on dashboard with all five scores; detail panel shows session history; extension tests pass\n\nRisk notes:\nSource data from dashboard-summary projection fixture (WBS-4A) before writing rollup render code","approach":"Add Brainstorming rollup (replacing New plan rollup) reading from brainstormingIdeas projection section. Display five scores. Update detail panel to show session history.","dependsOn":["T100788","T100789"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon (dashboard webview rollup, detail panel)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Brainstorming rollup displays all five synthesized scores for brainstorming-state ideas","New plan rollup replaced","Detail panel shows per-session and synthesized scores"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-4C","wbsPath":"4.3","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
