{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-40d0a509-cebf-4ca8-97d6-c66a49f1c58d","sequence":2381,"parentEventId":"evt-ebe96963-5aaf-48d9-bc45-5eca1d978743","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100792","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Manual agent task. Read I### rows and plan artifact files. Merge into unified format with correct status mapping. Dry-run first, then commit.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-6 (6) — Migrate existing Ideas and PlanArtifacts to unified document format\n\nApproach:\nManual agent task. Read each existing I### row from SQLite. For rows with a linked plan artifact, read the plan artifact JSON and merge into the unified document plan section with status mapped correctly. For rows without a linked plan artifact, promote to unified document format with status idea. Run dry-run first. Snapshot existing data to .workspace-kit/migration-backups/<timestamp>/ before any writes (rollback runbook in .ai/runbooks/unified-model-rollback.md covers restore procedure — see WBS-8). Commit only after dry-run validates clean.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- US-6\n\nTechnical scope:\n- .workspace-kit/ (SQLite ideas table — read existing I### rows)\n- .workspace-kit/planning/plan-artifacts/ (read existing plan artifact JSON files)\n- .workspace-kit/planning/plan-artifacts/ (write new unified document artifact files for each idea; update linked_plan_artifact on each SQLite ideas row)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- All existing I### rows have a linked_plan_artifact reference pointing to a new unified document artifact file in the correct format with status mapped correctly\n- Existing plan artifact JSON files merged into corresponding unified documents\n- Dry-run verified clean before commit — no data loss reported\n- Post-migration: get-idea returns schema-valid unified documents for all existing ideas\n\nVerification:\n- Dry-run reports all ideas and migration outcomes before any writes\n- Post-migration: get-idea on 3–5 existing ideas returns schema-valid unified documents per the per-state schema for their current status\n\nDone means:\nAll existing ideas and plan artifacts in unified document format; post-migration validation passes; no legacy split-model data remains\n\nRisk notes:\nLow volume makes this safe; dry-run is the key safety gate; schedule before dashboard deploy","approach":"Manual agent task. Read I### rows and plan artifact files. Merge into unified format with correct status mapping. Dry-run first, then commit.","dependsOn":["T100780","T100783"],"technicalScope":[".workspace-kit/ (SQLite ideas table, plan artifact files)"],"acceptanceCriteria":["All I### rows in unified document format with correct status post-migration","Dry-run verified clean before commit","get-idea returns schema-valid unified documents for all existing ideas"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-6","wbsPath":"6","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
