{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-6d56df04-4f00-4c77-9687-257d3a403051","sequence":2383,"parentEventId":"evt-6d49fbea-76ac-42cf-be77-f503f6b3bb8d","recordedAt":"2026-07-02T06:03:57.473Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100793","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Author plan-document.view.yaml and plan-document.md template. Implement generate-plan-document command: reads unified plan artifact, renders to docs/maintainers/plans/<ideaId>-<slug>.md using the view and template.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-7A (7.1) — Plan document view, template, and generate-plan-document command\n\nApproach:\nAuthor src/modules/documentation/views/plan-document.view.yaml defining the rendered sections: document header (status badge, idea id, title), brainstorm synthesis scores (Value/Risk/Effort/Confidence/Priority with color-band labels), brainstorm session history table, plan goals and non-goals, WBS summary table (id, title, dependencies, sizing), risk register, assumptions, open questions (if any), delivery refs, and provenance/version footer. Author src/modules/documentation/templates/plan-document.md as the markdown template for the view. Implement generate-plan-document command in the planning module: takes a planId, reads the unified plan artifact from the linked_plan_artifact path, renders it using the plan-document view and template, and writes the output to docs/maintainers/plans/<ideaId>-<slug>.md (slug derived from identity.title, lowercase, hyphenated, max 60 chars). Command returns the output path and a render summary. Add instruction .md file.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Every plan lifecycle event (draft persisted, reviewed, accepted, finalized) regenerates a human-readable plan document in docs/maintainers/plans/ via the documentation module infrastructure\n- A single document traces an idea from inception through brainstorming, planning, review, acceptance, and delivery — no separate entities to keep in sync\n- US-4\n\nTechnical scope:\n- src/modules/documentation/views/plan-document.view.yaml (new)\n- src/modules/documentation/templates/plan-document.md (new)\n- src/modules/planning/ (generate-plan-document command handler)\n- src/modules/planning/instructions/generate-plan-document.md (new)\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- plan-document.view.yaml defines all required rendered sections in display order\n- plan-document.md template renders valid markdown with no unresolved placeholders for a complete unified document fixture\n- generate-plan-document command reads unified plan artifact by planId and writes rendered markdown to docs/maintainers/plans/<ideaId>-<slug>.md\n- Output file slug is derived deterministically from ideaId and identity.title (lowercase, hyphenated, max 60 chars)\n- Brainstorm synthesis scores rendered with correct color-band labels (red/amber/green per score semantics)\n- WBS summary table includes all WBS items with id, title, sizing confidence, and dependsOn\n- generate-plan-document instruction .md file documents command usage, output path convention, and re-run behavior\n\nVerification:\n- Unit test: generate-plan-document produces a valid markdown file for a fixture unified document at accepted state\n- Unit test: output path slug is correct for a title with spaces, capitals, and punctuation\n- Unit test: brainstorm synthesis section renders with correct color-band labels for known score values\n- Unit test: WBS summary table contains all WBS items from fixture\n\nDone means:\ngenerate-plan-document command renders a complete markdown plan document from a unified plan artifact; view and template committed; instruction .md committed\n\nRisk notes:\nTemplate rendering must handle partial documents correctly — a plan in brainstorming state has no plan section yet; template must render gracefully with only the sections present at the current state","approach":"Author plan-document.view.yaml and plan-document.md template. Implement generate-plan-document command: reads unified plan artifact, renders to docs/maintainers/plans/<ideaId>-<slug>.md using the view and template.","dependsOn":["T100786","T100791"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/documentation/views/plan-document.view.yaml","src/modules/documentation/templates/plan-document.md","src/modules/planning/ (generate-plan-document handler)","src/modules/planning/instructions/generate-plan-document.md"],"acceptanceCriteria":["generate-plan-document writes rendered markdown to docs/maintainers/plans/<ideaId>-<slug>.md","Template renders all sections gracefully for any document state (partial documents handled)","Brainstorm synthesis scores rendered with color-band labels","Instruction .md documents usage and re-run behavior"],"phase":"Phase 140","phaseKey":"140","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningProvenance":{"planId":"f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planVersion":19,"wbsId":"WBS-7A","wbsPath":"7.1","planRef":"plan-artifact:f7a3b891-c5d2-4e6f-9a08-1b2c3d4e5f60","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I005","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"140"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
