igest into buildIdeaPlanningPrompt.\n5. Allow session completion on rich ideation even when not all 13 scores are filled (scores become optional convergent step).\n6. Create unified IdeaPlan document on create-idea (stop requiring global migrate-ideas-to-unified-document for new ideas).\n\n# Dogfood evidence (I009 session 0)\n- Agent was not guided through ideation; it bulk-filled measurables in one CLI call.\n- All qualitative content was crammed into sessionNotes because structured fields do not exist.\n- create-idea did not create a unified document; migrate-ideas-to-unified-document was required (also stamped I006/I008).\n- Migration dry-run documented as Tier C but runtime required policyApproval + expectedPlanningGeneration.\n\n# Implementation touchpoints\nschemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json, schemas/ideas/states/brainstorming.schema.json, src/modules/ideas/idea-plan-types.ts, update-brainstorm-session-handler.ts, complete-brainstorm-handler.ts, idea-plan-planning-init.ts, build-idea-planning-prompt.ts, create-idea handler (per-idea doc init), tests. Keep backward compatibility for existing sessions (I005, I007).\n\n# Scores (session 0)\nValue 7.6 | Risk 3.85 | Effort 6 | Confidence 7.3 | Priority 67 | Size M | Complexity 6\n\nUnified document: plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","status":"planning","sortOrder":8,"linkedPlanArtifact":"plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","previousPlanArtifacts":[],"createdAt":"2026-07-07T21:27:12.540Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-07T21:36:51.281Z"}}}
