{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-d07fedf9-a7d6-4b21-825b-c6dc77ce46f9","sequence":2524,"parentEventId":"evt-4c391c08-2857-47d9-863d-39185d2af690","recordedAt":"2026-07-07T21:48:10.742Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"create-task","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100807","changedFields":["summary","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Replace survey-only brainstorming with guided ideation chat, structured session storage, plan seeding, per-idea document init, and dashboard projection sync.","technicalScope":["schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json and states/brainstorming.schema.json (ideation fields + directive reframe)","src/modules/ideas/update-brainstorm-session-handler.ts, complete-brainstorm-handler.ts, idea-plan-planning-init.ts, build-idea-planning-prompt.ts, create-idea handler, validate-brainstorm-section.ts","src/modules/ideas/idea-plan-artifact-storage.ts (index sync on write; reconcile helper)","src/modules/task-engine/dashboard/build-dashboard-base.ts (unified plan title/summary fallback)","tests for ideation persistence, plan seeding, index sync, and dashboard summary"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Structured ideation fields persist through update-brainstorm-session without being dropped by the handler allowlist","Brainstorming agentDirective supports agent-contribution turns and per-turn save-vs-finish checkpoint guidance","complete-brainstorm and planning init seed plan.summary/goals/openQuestions/assumptions from brainstorm content; buildIdeaPlanningPrompt includes a brainstorm digest","create-idea auto-creates and links a unified IdeaPlan document without requiring migrate-ideas-to-unified-document","IdeaPlan writes keep the plan-artifact SQLite index current; dashboard-summary shows plan.title and plan.summary from unified documents","Existing brainstorm sessions (e.g. I005, I007) continue to validate after schema changes"],"metadata":{"issue":"Ideas brainstorming is a scoring survey with no guided ideation chat, no structured storage for agent-generated content, no mechanical plan seeding, and stale dashboard projection for unified IdeaPlan documents.","supportingReasoning":"Dogfood on I009 (plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810): agent bulk-filled scores without guided chat; qualitative output was crammed into sessionNotes; create-idea required global migration; dashboard showed generic \"Idea plan\" until index reconcile because IdeaPlan writes never updated plan-artifact index rows.","sourceIdeaId":"I009","linkedPlanRef":"plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810"}}},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-64f49b03-2a04-45e4-94d5-ecf1dc0e637c","sequence":2525,"parentEventId":"evt-d07fedf9-a7d6-4b21-825b-c6dc77ce46f9","recordedAt":"2026-07-07T21:48:56.359Z","actor":{"id":"workspace-kit","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"update-idea","moduleId":"ideas"},"kind":"planning.idea.updated","payload":{"idea":{"id":"I009","title":"Make brainstorming a real guided ideation session that seeds the plan","note":"# Problem\nIdeas → Brainstorm → Plan models brainstorming as a scoring survey, not guided ideation. The agentDirective is a fixed 18-question form. Session storage is additionalProperties:false with only 13 numeric scores + 5 text fields; update-brainstorm-session silently drops anything off SESSION_INPUT_FIELDS. There is no structured home for agent-generated feature ideas, perspectives, expectations, or transcript. None of the brainstorm content seeds the plan: complete-brainstorm and buildInitialIdeaPlanPlanSection use hardcoded plan.summary strings; buildIdeaPlanningPrompt never mentions brainstorm; synthesis only blends numeric scores (60/40 recency).\n\n# Goal\nA natural guided chat where the agent contributes ideas, perspective, feature suggestions, and expectations; offers save-and-return vs finish-and-plan each turn; persists qualitative output in the session record; and uses it to stub the first plan draft on promotion.\n\n# Design (target)\n1. Split session data: scoring (existing measurables) + ideation object: featureIdeas[], perspectives[], expectations[], openThreads[], decisions[], optional transcript[] ({role,text,at}).\n2. Reframe agentDirective: add agent-contribution turns (proposals/perspectives), not only elicit-from-operator questions.\n3. Per-turn checkpoint as first-class directive step (save partial session vs complete-brainstorm).\n4. Plan seed map on complete-brainstorm: featureIdeas→goals/userStories, openThreads→openQuestions, perspectives→assumptions/valueAssessment, notes→plan.summary; inject brainstorm digest into buildIdeaPlanningPrompt.\n5. Allow session completion on rich ideation even when not all 13 scores are filled (scores become optional convergent step).\n6. Create unified IdeaPlan document on create-idea (stop requiring global migrate-ideas-to-unified-document for new ideas).\n7. Dashboard projection: sync plan-artifact index on IdeaPlan writes; dashboard-summary reads plan.title/plan.summary from unified documents; reconcile helper for backfill.\n\n# Dashboard projection (dogfood)\nIdeaPlan writes did not refresh plan-artifact SQLite index rows, so dashboard Plans showed generic \"Idea plan\" until reconcile. Fix in flight: index upsert on write + dashboard-summary reads plan.title/plan.summary from unified documents. Tracked in plan v6 and improvement task T100807.\n\n# Dogfood evidence (I009 session 0)\n- Agent was not guided through ideation; it bulk-filled measurables in one CLI call.\n- All qualitative content was crammed into sessionNotes because structured fields do not exist.\n- create-idea did not create a unified document; migrate-ideas-to-unified-document was required (also stamped I006/I008).\n- Migration dry-run documented as Tier C but runtime required policyApproval + expectedPlanningGeneration.\n- Dashboard showed generic \"Idea plan\" until index reconcile.\n\n# Implementation touchpoints\nschemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json, schemas/ideas/states/brainstorming.schema.json, src/modules/ideas/idea-plan-types.ts, update-brainstorm-session-handler.ts, complete-brainstorm-handler.ts, idea-plan-planning-init.ts, build-idea-planning-prompt.ts, create-idea handler (per-idea doc init), idea-plan-artifact-storage.ts (index sync), build-dashboard-base.ts, tests. Keep backward compatibility for existing sessions (I005, I007).\n\n# Tracking\nImprovement task: T100807\nUnified document: plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810 (plan v6)","status":"planning","sortOrder":8,"linkedPlanArtifact":"plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","previousPlanArtifacts":[],"createdAt":"2026-07-07T21:27:12.540Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-07T21:48:56.358Z"}}}
{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-c1c4cbb6-daf1-4c77-9259-9d0550cf8618","sequence":2526,"parentEventId":"evt-64f49b03-2a04-45e4-94d5-ecf1dc0e637c","recordedAt":"2026-07-07T22:10:34.909Z","actor":{"id":"workspace-kit","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"update-idea","moduleId":"ideas"},"kind":"planning.idea.updated","payload":{"idea":{"id":"I009","title":"Make brainstorming a real guided ideation session that seeds the plan","note":"# Problem\nIdeas → Brainstorm → Plan models brainstorming as a scoring survey, not guided ideation.\n\n# Goal\nGuided ideation chat that seeds the plan draft.\n\n# Tracking\nT100807 | plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810 (v8)\n\n## Operator decisions (open questions resolved)\n- **D-1 Transcript:** Curated-only default; transcript opt-in per session (1-A).\n- **D-2 featureIdeas shape:** Plain string[] (2-B). Follow-up: align schema with shipped rationale-object impl.\n- **D-3 Multi-session synthesis:** synthesizeBrainstormIdeation() before promotion (3-B).\n- **D-4 Completion paths:** Ideation-complete OR scoring-complete (4-B; scoring UX-not-cheap).\n- **D-5 Dashboard:** Rich Ideas-card ideation snippets (5-C); extends I005 rollup scope.\nPlan artifact v8; WBS-7 added for synthesis + dashboard rollup.","status":"planning","sortOrder":8,"linkedPlanArtifact":"plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","previousPlanArtifacts":[],"createdAt":"2026-07-07T21:27:12.540Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-07T22:10:34.909Z"}}}
{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-78730c7a-61a1-4711-8a0a-aafb205edc2f","sequence":2527,"parentEventId":"evt-c1c4cbb6-daf1-4c77-9259-9d0550cf8618","recordedAt":"2026-07-07T22:23:16.513Z","actor":{"id":"workspace-kit","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"update-idea","moduleId":"ideas"},"kind":"planning.idea.updated","payload":{"idea":{"id":"I009","title":"Make brainstorming a real guided ideation session that seeds the plan","note":"# Problem\nIdeas brainstorming is a scoring survey, not guided ideation.\n\n# Goal\nGuided ideation chat that seeds the plan draft.\n\n# Execution policy\nWBS materializes tasks at finalize/execute only (PQ-11). T100807 cancelled — superseded by WBS-1..7.\n\n# Locked decisions\nD-1..D-5 and PQ-6..PQ-12 recorded on plan v10+ and brainstorm session.\n\n# Tracking\nplan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","status":"planning","sortOrder":8,"linkedPlanArtifact":"plan-artifact:08de149e-e528-4404-9e3a-885870fdf810","previousPlanArtifacts":[],"createdAt":"2026-07-07T21:27:12.540Z","updatedAt":"2026-07-07T22:23:16.513Z"}}}
