{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-bd4b313e-c449-4f42-a545-4ba44f7f1266","sequence":2530,"parentEventId":"evt-68d31517-948b-4190-a783-949804e8b11e","recordedAt":"2026-07-08T00:27:32.392Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100808","changedFields":["summary","description","approach","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"summary":"Extend brainstorm-session schema/types; parse and merge ideation in update-brainstorm-session.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-1 — Ideation schema and session persistence\n\nApproach:\nExtend brainstorm-session schema/types; parse and merge ideation in update-brainstorm-session; allow ideation-rich planning validation. Add ideationComplete flag on operator checkpoint confirmation (PQ-6). Align featureIdeas/decisions to string[] (PQ-8-A).\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Operators get a guided ideation brainstorm with agent contributions and save/finish checkpoints\n\nTechnical scope:\n- schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json\n- src/modules/ideas/brainstorm-ideation.ts\n- src/modules/ideas/update-brainstorm-session-handler.ts\n- src/modules/ideas/validate-brainstorm-section.ts\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- update-brainstorm-session persists ideation fields per PQ-8 shapes\n- ideationComplete:true is set only on operator-confirmed checkpoint (PQ-6)\n- validateBrainstormSectionForPlanning accepts ideationComplete OR scoring-complete\n\nVerification:\n- test/brainstorm-ideation.test.mjs\n- test/start-brainstorm-session.test.mjs\n\nDone means:\nStructured ideation survives session updates and validates for planning promotion.","approach":"Extend brainstorm-session schema/types; parse and merge ideation in update-brainstorm-session.","technicalScope":["schemas/ideas/brainstorm-session.schema.json","src/modules/ideas/brainstorm-ideation.ts","src/modules/ideas/update-brainsto