{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-95bf2ae6-8e64-4645-b1ee-655cc17cf355","sequence":2819,"parentEventId":"evt-ab00edba-20c8-4baf-89a1-3053bf968eb3","recordedAt":"2026-07-09T19:46:56.519Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100844","changedFields":["priority","summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"priority":"P1","summary":"Sequence opportunistic cache then CLI bootstrap after shell paint; adapt payloads into existing store hydrate shape; never wait on cold service.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-2 (2) — Cold-path bootstrap: CLI-primary with opportunistic cache and thin adapter\n\nApproach:\nImplement cold-path sequencing after shell paint: try reusable last-good cache if present, otherwise CLI bootstrap. Add a thin BootstrapSnapshotAdapter that maps cache/CLI/service payloads into the existing store hydrate shape. Do not block on service start. Keep the hydrate payload overview-minimal (phase/status + queue counts).\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Dashboard overview becomes usable within 3 seconds of shell paint when the service is cold or unavailable\n- Cold first paint uses CLI bootstrap as the guaranteed path; last-good cache only if already reusable\n\nTechnical scope:\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src\n- dashboard bootstrap/CLI snapshot path\n- dashboard data store hydrate path\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- With service unavailable, overview hydrates from CLI (or opportunistic cache) without waiting on service health\n- BootstrapSnapshotAdapter normalizes sources into one hydrate shape without a new data plane\n- Cold CLI bootstrap payload is overview-minimal (phase/status + queue counts only); Ideas/detail hydrate later\n- Usable overview includes phase/status, queue counts, and clears stuck loading shell; Ideas/detail may load later\n\nVerification:\n- Stubbed cold-service test hydrates overview from CLI within 3s budget using fake timers\n- Adapter unit tests for cache/CLI/service payload normalization\n- Assert cold CLI bootstrap path does not await Ideas/detail before clearing the loading shell\n\nDone means:\nCLI-primary cold bootstrap paints usable overview within budget with overview-minimal payload (mitigates R-2).\n\nRisk notes:\nR-2: CLI-only cold path must stay overview-minimal to hold the 3s budget when no cache exists.","approach":"Sequence opportunistic cache then CLI bootstrap after shell paint; adapt payloads into existing store hydrate shape; never wait on cold service.","dependsOn":["T100843"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src","dashboard bootstrap/CLI snapshot path","dashboard data store hydrate path"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Service-unavailable cold path hydrates from CLI or opportunistic cache without waiting on service health","Cold CLI bootstrap is overview-minimal; Ideas/detail hydrate later","Usable overview clears stuck loading shell within the 3s budget path"],"phase":"Phase 146","phaseKey":"146","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningProvenance":{"planId":"60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planVersion":15,"wbsId":"WBS-2","wbsPath":"2","planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningType":"change","sourceIdeaId":"I012","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"146"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
