{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-cad85922-5b92-48d0-8382-30d80f0ad9ef","sequence":2823,"parentEventId":"evt-0826ac63-d35f-4834-a621-f4250f7981e8","recordedAt":"2026-07-09T19:46:56.519Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100846","changedFields":["priority","summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"priority":"P1","summary":"Force service-unavailable; stub CLI/cache; fake timers; assert usable overview within 3s.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-4 (4) — Prove ≤3s cold-path first-paint SLA with deterministic tests\n\nApproach:\nAdd focused tests that force service-unavailable, drive the startup controller with stubbed CLI/cache reads and fake timers, and assert overview usable within 3s of shell paint. Document the usable-overview field checklist in the test assertions.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Dashboard overview becomes usable within 3 seconds of shell paint when the service is cold or unavailable\n\nTechnical scope:\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/test\n- test/\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- Automated cold-path test asserts usable overview within 3s using fake timers/stubs\n- Test does not depend on live dashboard-service startup timing\n- Assertions cover phase/status, queue counts, and absence of stuck loading shell\n- Cold-path SLA test fails if overview hydration waits on Ideas/detail or non-overview bootstrap work\n\nVerification:\n- New cold-path first-paint test passes in CI\n- Existing dashboard render/startup tests still pass\n- Negative/stub case proves SLA assertion trips when overview hydration is delayed past 3s\n\nDone means:\nDeterministic cold-path SLA tests prove ≤3s usable overview and catch budget regressions (mitigates R-2).\n\nRisk notes:\nR-2: Keep stubs narrow so the SLA test fails on real regressions (payload bloat / blocked awaits), not timer noise.","approach":"Force service-unavailable; stub CLI/cache; fake timers; assert usable overview within 3s.","dependsOn":["T100843","T100844","T100845"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/test","test/"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Cold-path test asserts usable overview within 3s with fake timers/stubs","Test does not depend on live dashboard-service startup timing","Negative case fails when overview hydration is delayed past 3s"],"phase":"Phase 146","phaseKey":"146","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningProvenance":{"planId":"60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planVersion":15,"wbsId":"WBS-4","wbsPath":"4","planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningType":"change","sourceIdeaId":"I012","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"146"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
