{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-2abe5759-4fbf-4380-9c12-f104b6ba5959","sequence":2825,"parentEventId":"evt-d1bcb437-b277-4e1b-87fd-5d22cc57984d","recordedAt":"2026-07-09T19:46:56.519Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100847","changedFields":["priority","summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"priority":"P1","summary":"Implement empty / first-run / no-data overview behavior on the CLI-primary cold path so fresh workspaces still paint a usable overview without waiting on the dashboard service.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-5 (5) — Empty and first-run overview behavior for cold bootstrap\n\nApproach:\nDefine and implement empty / first-run / no-data overview behavior on the CLI-primary cold path: fresh workspace and blank queue states must still paint a usable overview (phase/status line, zeroed or empty queue counts, no stuck loading shell) without waiting on the dashboard service.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Usable overview within 3s without a stuck loading shell, including empty/first-run workspaces\n\nTechnical scope:\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/dashboard\n- empty and first-run overview fixtures\n- BootstrapSnapshotAdapter empty/no-data mapping\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- Fresh workspace / first-run cold path paints usable overview with empty or zero queue counts and no stuck loading shell\n- No-data / blank queue states remain readable and do not block shell-painted to hydrated transition\n- Deterministic test covers empty and first-run overview behavior with stubbed CLI/cache reads\n\nVerification:\n- Unit/integration test for empty and first-run cold-path overview with stubbed CLI reads\n- Assert no stuck loading shell when queue counts are empty or zero\n\nDone means:\nEmpty and first-run cold paths paint a usable overview and are covered by deterministic tests.\n\nRisk notes:\nEmpty-state UX can be missed if fixtures only cover populated queues.","approach":"Implement empty / first-run / no-data overview behavior on the CLI-primary cold path so fresh workspaces still paint a usable overview without waiting on the dashboard service.","dependsOn":["T100844","T100846"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/dashboard","empty and first-run overview fixtures","BootstrapSnapshotAdapter empty/no-data mapping"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Fresh workspace / first-run cold path paints usable overview with empty or zero queue counts and no stuck loading shell","No-data / blank queue states remain readable and do not block shell-painted to hydrated transition","Deterministic test covers empty and first-run overview behavior with stubbed CLI/cache reads"],"phase":"Phase 146","phaseKey":"146","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningProvenance":{"planId":"60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planVersion":15,"wbsId":"WBS-5","wbsPath":"5","planRef":"plan-artifact:60075304-3c0c-46c6-9c8f-468dd8ef6379","planningType":"change","sourceIdeaId":"I012","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"146"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
