y require without parent pre-read\n\nVerification:\n- test/file-bug-report.test.mjs\n\nDone means:\nAgents can file rich proposed improvements through task engine without interactive policyApproval.\n\nRisk notes:\nR109 policy-model change — already operator-confirmed for this plan","approach":"Implement file-bug-report that creates type=improvement status=proposed via task-engine create path; hard-reject ready/other types; auto-read expectedPlanningGeneration under policy require; support evidenceKey/clientMutationId dedupe; accept structured rich evidence (symptom, command, code, remediation, relatedTaskId, issueKind) into metadata.issue/supportingReasoning; mark policySensitivity non-sensitive.","dependsOn":["T100849"],"technicalScope":["src/modules/agent-bug-reporting/","src/contracts/builtin-run-command-manifest.json","src/core/policy.ts","schemas/planning-generation-cli-prelude.json"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Happy path creates improvement@proposed with rich metadata","status=ready or non-improvement fails closed","Idempotent replay returns existing taskId","Works under planningGenerationPolicy require without parent pre-read"],"phase":"Phase 147","phaseKey":"147","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:5215726a-5278-47f2-a9ae-9df48594dc47","planningProvenance":{"planId":"5215726a-5278-47f2-a9ae-9df48594dc47","planVersion":24,"wbsId":"WBS-2","planRef":"plan-artifact:5215726a-5278-47f2-a9ae-9df48594dc47","planningType":"new-feature","sourceIdeaId":"I010","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"147"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
