iation copy when adminMutations/registry gates block writes\n\nVerification:\n- Extension unit/UI tests for drawer field set and post-success open path\n- Manual smoke: Duplicate a default runbook from Dashboard CAE and confirm file opens under .ai/cae/artifacts/\n\nDone means:\nOperators can create/copy workspace artifacts file-first without webview body editing\n\nRisk notes:\nDrawer must still satisfy backend required fields for create/duplicate","approach":"Replace rich create/update form body editing with a minimal identity drawer (type/id/title and required create fields only) on the Dashboard CAE Library. On success, call existing create/duplicate commands and auto-Open the returned path. Do not create activations. Do not send contentMarkdown from the Library primary path.","dependsOn":["T100871"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/guidance/guidance-authoring-extension-side.ts","extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/guidance/render-guidance-panel.ts","extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/dashboard/dashboard-input-drawer.js"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Create and Duplicate collect identity fields only (no markdown body field)","Successful Create/Duplicate opens the workspace artifact file in the editor","No activation is created as a side effect","Mutation failures still surface existing remediation copy when adminMutations/registry gates block writes"],"phase":"Phase 151","phaseKey":"151","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planningProvenance":{"planId":"fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planVersion":18,"wbsId":"WBS-2","wbsPath":"2","planRef":"plan-artifact:fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planningType":"change","sourceIdeaId":"I013","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"151"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
