{"schemaVersion":1,"eventId":"evt-3d9f9329-be90-4582-83d8-e5fcaacad51b","sequence":3102,"parentEventId":"evt-e474e154-5c15-41c8-acac-99caad23b28b","recordedAt":"2026-07-16T21:04:31.866Z","actor":{"id":"NJLaPrell@gmail.com","source":"system"},"command":{"name":"persist-planning-execution-drafts","moduleId":"task-engine"},"kind":"task.updated","payload":{"taskId":"T100874","changedFields":["priority","summary","description","approach","dependsOn","technicalScope","acceptanceCriteria","phase","phaseKey","metadata"],"values":{"priority":"P2","summary":"Expand render-guidance / Dashboard CAE tests for Library framing, absent stubs/textarea, Create/Duplicate field set, and Reveal routing. Keep operator-facing notes in the Dashboard CAE Library empty-state using the locked WBS-3 copy. Name post-v1 follow-ups only as out-of-scope.","description":"Plan WBS row: WBS-4 (4) — Library regression coverage + in-product notes\n\nApproach:\nExpand render-guidance / Dashboard CAE tests for Library framing, absent stubs/textarea, Create/Duplicate field set, and Reveal routing. Keep operator-facing notes in the Dashboard CAE Library empty-state using the locked WBS-3 copy. Name post-v1 follow-ups only as out-of-scope.\n\nGoal mapping:\n- Operators can discover cae.* and workspace.* artifacts for all six CAE types from one Library surface\n- Operators open and edit workspace artifact bodies in the real editor, not a webview markdown textarea\n- Operators can Copy default→workspace or Create workspace artifacts with identity-only input, then land in the editor\n- Empty-state and Reveal teach the shared .ai/cae/artifacts/ tree without hard-gating browse\n\nTechnical scope:\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/test/render-guidance.test.mjs\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/guidance/render-guidance.ts\n- extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/dashboard\n\nAcceptance criteria:\n- Automated tests cover Library no-textarea, no-stub-buttons, and Reveal/Create intent on Dashboard CAE\n- In-product copy matches locked empty-state strings and mentions Open/Reveal/Copy/Create + .ai/cae/artifacts/\n- Post-v1 follow-ups (rebind, hide/override) are named only as out-of-scope notes, not acceptance\n\nVerification:\n- pnpm exec node --test extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/test/render-guidance.test.mjs\n- Spot-check Library empty-state copy in Dashboard CAE tab\n\nDone means:\nv1 Library behavior is regression-guarded and operators can discover the workflow from Dashboard CAE\n\nRisk notes:\nKeep notes in-product on Dashboard CAE; avoid maintainer docs churn for this slice","approach":"Expand render-guidance / Dashboard CAE tests for Library framing, absent stubs/textarea, Create/Duplicate field set, and Reveal routing. Keep operator-facing notes in the Dashboard CAE Library empty-state using the locked WBS-3 copy. Name post-v1 follow-ups only as out-of-scope.","dependsOn":["T100872","T100873"],"technicalScope":["extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/test/render-guidance.test.mjs","extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/guidance/render-guidance.ts","extensions/cursor-workflow-cannon/src/views/dashboard"],"acceptanceCriteria":["Automated tests cover Library no-textarea, no-stub-buttons, and Reveal/Create intent on Dashboard CAE","In-product copy matches locked empty-state strings and mentions Open/Reveal/Copy/Create + .ai/cae/artifacts/","Post-v1 follow-ups (rebind, hide/override) are named only as out-of-scope notes, not acceptance"],"phase":"Phase 151","phaseKey":"151","metadata":{"planRef":"plan-artifact:fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planningProvenance":{"planId":"fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planVersion":18,"wbsId":"WBS-4","wbsPath":"4","planRef":"plan-artifact:fc42031e-d3e6-44f7-9989-4676c366ad6c","planningType":"change","sourceIdeaId":"I013","source":"persist-planning-execution-drafts"}}}},"workspace":{"phaseKey":"151"},"expectedTaskVersion":1}
